## Angular Material Design - Angular 1.3

https://github.com/angular/material

[Material Design](https://www.google.com/design/spec/material-design/) is a specification for a
unified system of visual, motion, and interaction design that adapts across different devices. angular/material is a lean, lightweight set of AngularJS-native UI elements that implement the
material design specification for use in Angular single-page applications (SPAs).

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2qiyhkQVyxE

